{
  "stem": "5551.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Actually, what he did is he was shoveling coal in the locomotive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But the locomotive went out of the camp into town, and it gave him a way to establish connections with the Polish people once again.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The Polish, at that point in time, had a mutual enemy with the Jews, and more and more of them were willing to be helpful, rather than to do them in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There were cases where the Polish denounced, did in, and so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The Germans knew how to provoke it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They-- they promised them privileges, a pound of sugar and so, and always warned the Polish, if you aid a Jew, you are in for execution.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This is under death penalty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So it's-- it's remarkable that-- the kind of help we got.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But my father established town connections, and because of it, we had a little more food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Food were essential for survival because it is apparent, and is now known, that the kind of diet that was served to the Jews in slave labor camps was meant to exterminate them in time, all in itself.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, what was the diet?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] We got soup, but the soup-- it depended very much on who you are in camp and who you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those who had some ins got at least a nourishing soup that was thicker and had some ingredients.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of it was garbage anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't any kind of food from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- it was whatever the Germans had as garbage was put into there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it had nutrients, and it kept us alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
